#: app/templates/help.html:7
msgid ""
"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli vključuje vgrajena navodila po celotni aplikaciji, ki vam pomagajo "
"pri konfiguraciji in upravljanju nastavitve."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran zagotavlja pregled ključnih funkcij in neposredne povezave do tega,"
" kje jih je mogoče upravljati."

